# Spine Python Bindings

Python bindings for the Spine bridge library.

## Installation

```bash
pip install .
```

## Usage

```python
from spine import Namespace, Subscriber
from mad import MadType

ns = Namespace("example", "key")
sub = Subscriber(ns, "topic", MadType.uint32)
data = sub.get_data()
```
